  "subject": "Disable scheduled maintenance branch docker builds",
  "commit_message": "Disable scheduled maintenance branch docker builds\n\n - separate new template for maintenance branches from\n   master job template (which remains scheduled)\n - disable maintenance jobs scheduling with empty cron\n - note that this should be only temporary workaround until\n   the affected dcaegen2 CSIT setups have been improved\nIssue-ID: DMAAP-1502\n\nSigned-off-by: Lasse Kaihlavirta <l.kaihlavirt@partner.samsung.com>\nChange-Id: If121a835b2f9f2d7f41c06ebc3dfeb0bc549486c\n",
